T1  - Technical, scale and allocative efficiencies of Turkish banking industry
AU  - Isik, Ihsan
AU  - Hassan, M.Kabir
JO  - Journal of Banking & Finance
VL  - 26
IS  - 4
SP  - 719
EP  - 766
PY  - 2002
